is part two of our three-part

00:00:25.970 --> 00:00:28.310
mini-series on Modern Egypt.

00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:30.980
In part one, in case you missed

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:33.009
it, we talked about the Egyptian

00:00:33.010 --> 00:00:35.480
Revolution, how Mubarak was toppled,

00:00:35.910 --> 00:00:37.670
and how what ultimately came

00:00:37.670 --> 00:00:39.949
next wasn’t all that different.

